rientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00178_024.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 台灣遠東油脂公司被揭使用過期原料生產人造牛油品牌「乳瑪琳」，共有906噸問題產品流入市面，該公司被裁罰款240萬元新台幣及追繳不法所得的800多萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00178_027.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170314%2F00178_027.html&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8cda5df7\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00178_027.html</a> (東方日報)"},{"pid":"02cbd283d4bbc8c7739107b26b2e9377a5e39d14","tid":155244,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:52:54.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 蘇格蘭民族黨黨魁兼蘇格蘭首席部長施雅晴宣佈，蘇格蘭將會尋求在2018年底至2019年初再度舉行脫英獨立公投。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428391874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428391874&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3aafad07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428391874&h=6f386a18\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428391874</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00180_011.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170314%2F00180_011.html&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=edbf37b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00180_011.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564656&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564656%26target%3D2&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c2f9d4ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564656%26target%3D2&h=6f686728\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564656&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 南韓軍方透露指，美國陸軍開始向駐韓美軍群山基地部署連級「灰鷹」無人攻擊機部隊，此機在軍情告急時可北飛平壤執行「斬首」任務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564668&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564668%26target%3D2&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=27658bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564668%26target%3D2&h=e9ef4e43\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564668&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 韓美聯合司令部宣佈，韓美「關鍵決斷」年度聯合軍演正式啟動，屆時美軍先進武器和大規模兵力將會參演，其會重點演練應對北韓方面的軍事活動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564671&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564671%26target%3D2&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3f45f7f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564671%26target%3D2&h=f375a5dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564671&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 沙特阿拉伯國王薩勒曼抵達東京，務求爭取日本三大銀行、豐田汽車、能源公司JX集團及東京證券交易所等進駐其經濟特區拓展商機，減低對石油的依賴。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428387521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428387521&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7e044cc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428387521&h=83e23320\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428387521</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 英國上下議院預期將在當地時間周一晚上通過啓動脫歐的議案，令首相文翠珊最早可於今日啟動《里斯本條約》第五十條，正式展開脫歐程序。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564662&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564662%26target%3D2&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8940e2b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1564662%26target%3D2&h=d3b02865\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1564662&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 非洲埃塞俄比亞發生大量垃圾傾塌掩埋鄰近寮屋事故，造成最少62人死亡、數十人失蹤、54人受傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428392622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428392622&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=daf9937a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170314%2Fs00014%2F1489428392622&h=8951c159\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170314/s00014/1489428392622</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170314/00180_028.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170314%2F00180_028.html&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=873306